room_description: A hike through the woods takes a frightening turn when you and your friends end up lost in the woods.  You stumble across a dimly lit cabin that you assume will be your saving grace, but that saving grace quickly turns into a haunting experience with a creature you can barely fend off.  After he traps you inside, you manage to push him to the basement, but time is ticking away faster and faster. Can you figure out how to escape before he breaks free or will the creature make his escape first?
